title: Episode #92 - Michael Yo & ME
description: Stand-up comic & TV persoanlity Michael Yo sits w/ me in the Mancave and talks about his start in Stand-up & TV, dinner w/ Tiger Woods, Chelsea Handler, playing football, & we pontificate about what it is like being a man.
